body:
* Rename _imei property by _identity.
* Event callback implementation. More events comming soon.
  - onConnect
  - onDisconnect
  - onLogin
  - onSendNickname
  - onSendPresence
  - onPing
  - onPong
  - onDissectPhone
  - onFailedDissectPhone
  - onGoodCredentials
  - onBadCredentials
* Add disconnect function.
* New message id implementation.
* Change dissectPhone function to protected.
* Fix Ping callback.
* Remove unused sendComposing function.
* Store accountinfo in login function.

commit.message: Event callback implementation. More events comming soon.
Add user phone number to all enents.
Add country argument in onDissectPhone event.
Remove sendNickname method to duplicate the function of sendPresence. Both did the same.
Fix array merge in onDissectPhone event.
Add support to send Places location.
Add some comments in Places location.
Add audio codec attribute onAudio event.
Add support to create chat groups and add/remove participants.

title: Event callback implementation.
